CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 9 reads: "Homemakers See Latest in Foods, Appliances...5. The beautiful Budweiser booth was represented by Samuel T. Ambrosia, Harold Weismantel, Wilford Vaux of St. Louis, Mo., and assisted by Miss Agnes Norvell...Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Samuel T. Ambrosia, Harold Weismantel, Wilford Vaux, and Agnes Norvell standing in Budweiser booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
